title: Cross Country Roundup: Fairfield Union Finishes Second
text:
Cross Country Roundup: Fairfield Union Finishes Second 10:53 p.m. EDT October 24, 2015 CONNECT TWEET LINKEDIN COMMENT EMAIL MORE 
District II District Meet 
Fairfield Union was led by third place finisher Emma Hoellrich in 19:43. Hoellrich’s teammates Jessica Swaim (7th, 20:00), Heather Lecrone (9th, 20:04), Dorothy King (14th, 21:09) and Monica Taylor (16th, 21:18) helped the team to a second place finish with 49 points. 
On the boys side, Fairfield Union was led by fifth place finisher Thomas Troup in 16:48. Troup’s teammates Dylan Smith (15th, 17:36), Michael Taylor (19th, 17:56), Andrew Wade (22nd, 18:09) and Logan Gaib (30th, 18:40) helped the team to a second place finish with 91 points.
